  "text": "The multiple regression model used in the current study was created for unilateral IRM recession. A previous study showed that the dose-effect relationship for EOM recession differed among the EOMs [CITATION_1] . The present model may, therefore, not be used for recession of the other EOMs. Future studies are necessary to determine other models for recession regarding the other EOMs.",
